cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CE 

This paper deals with machine learning models and their bias, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The specific application domain is paid search auctions, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of adversarial neural networks is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also deals with modeling and data analysis, which falls under the category of computational engineering (cs.CE).
